flowchart TD
    start([Start]) --> openDashboard[Admin or librarian opens dashboard]
    openDashboard --> checkRole{Logged in as admin or librarian?}
    checkRole -->|No| denyAccess[Redirect to login or show access denied]
    denyAccess --> endNode([End])
    checkRole -->|Yes| loadMetrics[Aggregate books, readers, todays borrow orders, top 5 books, overdue readers]

    loadMetrics --> showDashboard[Display overview dashboard]
    showDashboard --> chooseAction{Choose action}
    chooseAction -->|Refresh| refreshData[Reload dashboard data]
    chooseAction -->|Open detail report| openDetailReport[Go to detailed reports]
    chooseAction -->|Exit| endNode

    refreshData --> loadMetrics
    openDetailReport --> endNode
